{"tid":899273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如叫返支那做震旦(含典故)","createTime":"2018-11-12T09:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T10:29:44.000Z","uid":221265,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b61c45f564e1cb2af53df7e3c0252a4377bc29ff","tid":899273,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">震旦</span></span></strong>（梵語： Cīna-sthāna，巴利語： Cīna-rattha），又譯震丹、真丹、真旦、振旦、神丹，也稱摩訶震旦（Mahā-cīna-sthāna），漢傳佛教經典中，對古代中國的稱呼，義同秦斯坦(既秦王國)。這個稱呼可能源自中亞或印度。<br />\n現今中國有部分機構以震旦為名，如震旦集團、上海震旦職業學院、震旦博物館等。<br />\n<br />\n既然中國都有機構自稱震旦，咁不如改返叫佢哋做震旦，<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">國旗國歌都要改</span></strong>。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K80tWGZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK80tWGZ.png&h=04d7451c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v352gGZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv352gGZ.jpg&h=4c02e0ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGA2gG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGA2gG0.jpg&h=79a2f7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OPGdom0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPGdom0.jpg&h=e7e21118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBoGxfm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBoGxfm.jpg&h=c21f3a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQ9uF8G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQ9uF8G.jpg&h=482dc594&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eef7111098e3fec415c400b002c25b95dd85bb61","tid":899273,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b61c45f564e1cb2af53df7e3c0252a4377bc29ff","tid":899273,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-